      "question": "Refer to the exhibit.\nAn engineer must configure the interface that connects to PC1 and secure it in a way that only PC1\nis allowed to use the port. No VLAN tagging can be used except for a voice VLAN. Which command\nsequence must be entered to configure the switch?",
