        "C": "SW3",
        "D": "SW4"
      },
      "answer": [
        "C"
      ],
      "answer_images": [],
      "explanation": "The “login local” command instructs the device to use the username and password in its local\ndatabase for authentication. The secret is encrypted when it is stored on the local router.",
