      "type": "multi",
      "question": "Refer to the exhibit.\nA guest WLAN must be created that prompts the client for a username and password on the local\nweb page of the WLC. Which two actions must be performed on the Layer 2 tab before enabling\nthe Authentication option on the Layer 3 tab? (Choose two)",
      "question_images": [],
